MUNDO: All right,
you guys are our eyes.

33:21.367 --> 33:23.335
It's a mad house down here.

33:23.369 --> 33:27.373
(chanting):
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

33:27.406 --> 33:30.376
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

33:30.409 --> 33:33.812
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

33:33.845 --> 33:35.347
Okay, I think
we've got something.

33:35.381 --> 33:37.316
Elijah, 20 yards north,
across the street.

33:37.349 --> 33:38.517
Blue shirt, black hat.

33:40.086 --> 33:41.220
I got him.

33:41.253 --> 33:43.322
...justice knows no death.

33:43.355 --> 33:46.325
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

33:46.358 --> 33:49.495
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

33:49.528 --> 33:50.629
Where is Derek Noels?

33:50.662 --> 33:52.398
