Krummy, talk to me.

33:54.300 --> 33:55.334
Uh, okay, okay.

33:55.367 --> 33:56.635
Okay, okay, um...

33:56.668 --> 33:58.437
There he is, there he is,
to your left, Avery.

33:58.470 --> 33:59.471
He's right beside you.

34:00.572 --> 34:03.409
RAMIREZ:
Elijah, 3:00.

34:03.442 --> 34:04.510
...justice knows no death.

34:04.543 --> 34:05.544
Where is Derek Noels?

34:05.577 --> 34:06.745
Justice knows no death!

34:06.778 --> 34:08.414
Where is Derek Noels?

34:08.447 --> 34:09.748
RYAN: Hands up,
hands up, don't move.

34:09.781 --> 34:12.318
FBI, hands behind
your back now!

34:12.351 --> 34:13.552
Give me your
other hand!

34:13.585 --> 34:16.188
RYAN:
He wiped his phone.

34:16.222 --> 34:17.223
Stand back! Clear!

34:25.264 --> 34:27.433
(chanting):
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

34:30.536 --> 34:33.372
Mr. Gaines,
I'm Special Agent Avery Ryan.

34:33.405 --> 34:34.840
I'm with the FBI.

34:34.873 --> 34:36.342
May I please have some water?

34:36.375 --> 34:37.409
I have
a few questions.

34:37.443 --> 34:39.811
You answer them honestly,
you'll not only get water,

34:39.845 --> 34:41.813
I'll let you speak
to your wife, Nicole.

34:41.847 --> 34:43.215
How does that sound?

34:43.249 --> 34:44.683
You're good.

34:44.716 --> 34:48.587
I mean, you set the parameters
of what you want,

34:48.620 --> 34:51.457
use my wife as a lure
to ensure cooperation,

34:51.490 --> 34:53.892
even drop her first name to
put us on a personal level.

34:53.925 --> 34:55.561
It's impressive.

34:55.594 --> 34:57.429
Thanks.

34:57.463 --> 34:59.531
I read your thesis.

34:59.565 --> 35:00.899
I know it's a sick experiment,

35:00.932 --> 35:02.568
some twisted social game
you're playing,

35:02.601 --> 35:03.902
but why?

35:03.935 --> 35:05.571
This is no game, Agent Ryan.

35:05.604 --> 35:08.407
This is the evolution
of social science.

35:10.209 --> 35:12.178
I was able to predict
with absolute certainty

35:12.211 --> 35:14.680
the chain of events
which led to-to this moment.

35:16.848 --> 35:19.818
Mankind will benefit
because of us.

35:19.851 --> 35:22.288
And who is "us"?

35:22.321 --> 35:24.156
Derek and I.

35:24.190 --> 35:25.357
Derek Noels?

35:26.658 --> 35:28.294
He's a remarkable human being.

35:28.327 --> 35:32.564
Nine months ago, I met Derek
on a bus bound for New York.

35:32.598 --> 35:33.699
He poured his heart out.

35:33.732 --> 35:35.567
He... he shared his pain.

35:35.601 --> 35:39.238
And he told me a story about
how he was humiliated by a cop.

35:39.271 --> 35:42.941
Beaten... but never arrested.

35:42.974 --> 35:45.611
Derek was homeless and
unable to find a job.

35:45.644 --> 35:47.479
He was so broken
by the system

35:47.513 --> 35:48.614
that he just wanted
to disappear.

35:48.647 --> 35:49.948
So that's what inspired you

35:49.981 --> 35:51.817
to find the video
and post it online?

35:51.850 --> 35:54.686
That's not Derek in that video.

35:54.720 --> 35:56.688
The irony is--
is my brother had

35:56.722 --> 35:58.557
several videos to choose from.

35:58.590 --> 36:00.659
Destiny chose this one.

36:00.692 --> 36:02.828
So where's Derek now?
I don't know.

36:02.861 --> 36:04.696
Then who's the man
in that video?

36:04.730 --> 36:06.365
Does it matter?

36:06.398 --> 36:08.700
They're all Derek Noels.

36:08.734 --> 36:09.901
You're not racist.

36:09.935 --> 36:12.571
You're a coward.

36:12.604 --> 36:14.573
This isn't about science.

36:14.606 --> 36:17.509
This is about vengeance,
because you hate your brother.

36:18.977 --> 36:20.212
How do you think your wife,
Nicole, is gonna feel

36:20.246 --> 36:24.516
when she finds out her husband
is responsible for all of this?

36:26.385 --> 36:28.720
Enjoy reading
your thesis in prison.

36:28.754 --> 36:31.290
Only after bloodshed
is there healing.

36:32.758 --> 36:35.594
9/11, Sandy Hook,

36:35.627 --> 36:38.730
the Charleston
church shooting.

36:38.764 --> 36:40.766
It's the only way.

36:44.870 --> 36:47.373
RYAN:
Something is not right.

36:47.406 --> 36:50.542
He's extremely calm, much too
confident in the face of defeat.

36:50.576 --> 36:52.311
He's got another play.

36:52.344 --> 36:53.779
Did you get anything
off his phone?

36:53.812 --> 36:54.913
No, it was wiped clean.

36:54.946 --> 36:56.848
(indistinct chatter
about phones)

37:02.988 --> 37:04.623
Chief Richards,
what's going on?

37:04.656 --> 37:05.491
I'm on with Causley.

37:05.524 --> 37:06.725
The safe house has
been compromised.

37:06.758 --> 37:10.862
His GPS coordinates are being
sent to every phone in the city.

37:10.896 --> 37:12.264
His detail is headed
back to the precinct.

37:12.298 --> 37:13.465
RYAN:
This is his play.

37:13.499 --> 37:14.733
This is Gaines.

37:14.766 --> 37:16.802
He wanted to make sure that his
brother was slaughtered tonight.

37:16.835 --> 37:18.003
How's he doing
this, Nelson?

37:19.671 --> 37:21.773
NELSON: Has to be
an auto-dialer.

37:21.807 --> 37:24.009
Question is--
how'd he tag him?

37:24.042 --> 37:25.944
It's the GPS in the car,
it's got to be.

37:25.977 --> 37:27.946
Protocol is to sweep
the car before it moves.

37:27.979 --> 37:29.948
And the GPS is turned off...
It's the phones,

37:29.981 --> 37:31.850
The phones.
I need to talk to Causley.

37:34.453 --> 37:35.754
RYAN: Officer Causley, this is
Special Agent Ryan with the FBI.

37:35.787 --> 37:37.756
Listen to me carefully,
I need you and your detail

37:37.789 --> 37:39.458
to toss your phones now.

37:39.491 --> 37:41.460
You're being tracked.

37:41.493 --> 37:42.728
Phones.

37:44.830 --> 37:45.764
It's done.

37:46.932 --> 37:48.800
NELSON:
Didn't work.

37:48.834 --> 37:50.769
He's still tagged.

37:50.802 --> 37:52.904
The tracker has to be
on him, hidden.

37:52.938 --> 37:54.440
You two, get a team,
bring Causley back.

37:54.473 --> 37:56.475
On it.
RYAN: Officer Causley,

37:56.508 --> 37:58.777
I believe your brother
planted a tracker on you.

37:58.810 --> 37:59.778
It's small, it should be hidden

37:59.811 --> 38:01.647
on something he knows
you would keep with you.

38:07.586 --> 38:09.788
CAUSLEY: He hid the tracker
in my badge?

38:09.821 --> 38:11.557
Sneaky son of a...

38:14.059 --> 38:15.727
MAN: Oh, my God!
WOMAN: What was that?!

38:15.761 --> 38:17.363
Somebody call 911!
Hey, man.

38:17.396 --> 38:18.864
Isn't that that cop?

38:26.472 --> 38:28.039
Call an ambulance,
I've got Causley!

38:28.073 --> 38:30.008
NELSON: Hello?
Yo, listen, listen.

38:30.041 --> 38:32.010
We need an EMT over
at Avenue 24 and D Street.

38:32.043 --> 38:33.044
Hurry up! Come quick!

38:34.380 --> 38:35.447
Come on!

38:35.481 --> 38:37.583
That's the cop
that killed Derek Noels!

38:39.117 --> 38:40.719
Get back now!

38:41.853 --> 38:43.722
Come on!
MUNDO: Get him back
to the precinct, go!

38:47.092 --> 38:49.361
Stay back! Stay back!

39:03.475 --> 39:05.877
Hurry, hurry, the tracker.

39:05.911 --> 39:07.012
It's my badge, my badge.

39:07.045 --> 39:08.447
Get in.

39:15.421 --> 39:16.922
(tires screeching)

39:21.192 --> 39:23.995
(chanting):
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

39:24.029 --> 39:27.866
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

39:27.899 --> 39:30.869
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

39:30.902 --> 39:34.973
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

39:35.006 --> 39:39.010
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

39:39.044 --> 39:42.581
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

39:42.614 --> 39:45.851
Where is Derek Noels?
Justice knows no death!

39:45.884 --> 39:47.519
Where is Derek Noels?

39:47.553 --> 39:48.787
Get him out of sight.

39:48.820 --> 39:50.556
Are you two hurt?

39:50.589 --> 39:51.857
No.

39:51.890 --> 39:52.958
Yeah, we're good.

39:52.991 --> 39:56.094
Agent Ryan, thank you.
All of you.

39:56.127 --> 39:57.896
But I think it's best
if you and your team go.

39:59.030 --> 40:01.933
We're not going anywhere
until order is restored.

40:01.967 --> 40:03.969
RICHARDS: I appreciate
the sentiment.

40:04.002 --> 40:05.070
We don't have enough men
to hold City Hall.

40:05.103 --> 40:07.773
And the National Guard
won't arrive until morning.

